text.section:
"Affiliate" means any association, corporation, business trust, statutory trust, or other similar organization that:
Is not a bank service corporation and is controlled by a banking institution through:
Direct or indirect ownership or control of more than 50 percent of the voting rights;
Control of the election of a majority of the management;
Direct or indirect ownership or control of more than 50 percent of the voting rights exercised at the last election of the management;
Directors of the banking institution constituting a majority of the management of the organization; or
Any direct or indirect control by stockholders of the banking institution, if the stockholders own or control:
Controls a banking institution through:
Direct or indirect ownership or control of more than 50 percent of the voting rights;
Control of the election of a majority of the directors of the banking institution;
Direct or indirect ownership or control of more than 50 percent of the voting rights exercised at the last election of the directors; or
The holding of substantially all of the capital stock of the banking institution by trustees for stockholders of the organization.
